# ccfish bench node signature: the local bench set at fixed depth, NNUE loaded.
# Regenerate ONLY for an intended behaviour change, and say what moved it in the
# commit body. Updating this on a red gate launders a bug into the anchor.
#
# NOT upstream's bench. Upstream runs its full default position list to depth 13
# at Hash 16 with a single `ucinewgame`, and scores 2466447. Aligning this bench
# with that definition is the open task; until then this number is ccfish's own.
#
# REQUIRES THE NNUE NET -- `./build.sh signature` skips with exit 127 without one,
# because the classical fallback searches a different tree.
#
# Last re-derived when the ported search decomposition replaced the monolith:
# razoring, ProbCut, singular extensions and tt_pv-driven reductions all became
# live, which prunes far harder. perft was unchanged throughout.
48422
